    "AI can deploy and manage intricate statistical models like Bayesian networks, neural networks, and decision trees.",
    "For instance, neural networks can model complex nonlinear relationships in biological data, while Bayesian networks can elucidate probabilistic relationships in epidemiological studies.",
    "Furthermore, AI tools can automate data cleaning, preprocessing, and analysis, saving time and minimizing human error.",
    "Platforms such as IBM Watson and Google Cloud AutoML offer robust solutions for automated data analysis.",
    "Natural language processing (NLP) techniques can extract relevant information from extensive text bodies, like literature reviews or research articles."
